{"tid":1516494,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[代問]識左個日本囡囡 幾時要去馬?","createTime":"2019-08-29T14:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:57:56.000Z","uid":90073,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"97ccc6d60c097846d21ae2d34946b57dff9e20f3","tid":1516494,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"FD子無連登AC<br />\n幫問<br />\n佢識左個日本妹4~5個月<br />\n上個月同個架妹單獨出夜街<br />\n講野唔算好多<br />\n但可以摸手仔(NOT 拖) 同控好埋<br />\n應唔應該去馬"},{"pid":"cc6074fe7f0e09ce778f0b95c2b5017dfa5a33e0","tid":1516494,"uid":179292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:48:18.000Z","msg":"圖定老母"},{"pid":"579e1596365e671277fdc5d5adbac95f58c1afb0","tid":1516494,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc6074fe7f0e09ce778f0b95c2b5017dfa5a33e0","tid":1516494,"uid":179292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:48:18.000Z","msg":"圖定老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:49:26.000Z","msg":"幫FD子問<br />\n我都想要圖"},{"pid":"af789def915be0416ed7885c1efc799bf9d85c1c","tid":1516494,"uid":231818,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"f4949c090e6c095dbc1446f44f850ae2ffb90ae2","tid":1516494,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:52:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c10c82ffc2538ed2ffc652d9c25e1fc4a7bd058","tid":1516494,"uid":283900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"其實日本妹好開放 拖勁耐都唔敢行動佢地會覺得你廢<br />\n<br />\n以前住過日本 身邊唔少日本朋友"},{"pid":"5874d7ea6a376c041c1dc719f772c8fb62b19ac7","tid":1516494,"uid":90073,"lik